preference.name: CommercialPart_PseudoFolder
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of properties that can be displayed as a pseudo folder under a node for a CommercialPart object. The preference must be enabled to let the user view and manage the dataset associated with a commercial part. Valid Values: Accepts one or more strings as values.
